  "commentary": "With SPX at 6818.91 sitting right in the heart of massive negative gamma between 6800-6820, dealers are being forced to buy this dip aggressively as their short gamma positions demand same-direction hedging. The breakout regime combined with the wall break and GEX surge signals we're in full amplification mode - dealers will continue buying any weakness toward 6800 and selling any strength above 6840 where positive gamma kicks in. Watch 6820 closely as the max negative gamma strike; a decisive break below triggers accelerated dealer buying into the 6800-6810 zone.\n\nBottom line: expect volatile swings with dealer buying supporting dips toward 6800 but selling capping rallies above 6840.",
